reviewText: Has some great flicks. Some are a bit old but good ones to add to my collection.
I bought this for "Last Action Hero"...the rest were "freebies".
8 nice but not great flicks.  4 on each disc-all on one side-all widescreen.  You could do alot worse, so go buy and enjoy!
Nice collection. I bought mainly for Silent Rage.

To be honest I only purchased this for The Chuck Norris movie Silent Rage. Saw that movie when it released in theatres back in the very early 1980s. The last action hero movie is probably the worst movie Armold Ever made lol. Overall a good purchase though, and would recommend if you are into action movies.
Bought this disc to get one movie, but, it was cheaper to purchase it this way than by itself.
A 3 STARS RATING IS GENEROUS.  COLOR TRANSFER IS LOUSY,  A FEW MOVIES HAD BACKGROUND NOISE AND STREAKS. STORIES WERE OK. THE GOOD THING WAS "IT WASN'T EXPENSIVE"
shipped on time good selection of movies although I got it for silent rage I watched them all
good value for price, 8 good action flicks
bought it for stone killer  starring Charles Bronson the rest were along for the ride
